{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/boxerjs/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"CodeSpud","author":"@codespud"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8a811d58-91be-5b1f-b87c-8082a8096722","excerpt":"A lightweight jQuery plugin that turns links to images into quick inline previews. BoxerJS wraps image links so they open as fast previews…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>A lightweight jQuery plugin that turns links to images into quick inline previews.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>BoxerJS wraps image links so they open as fast previews instead of full page loads. It supports images and HTML snippets loaded over AJAX. See the demo for live examples.</p>\n<p><strong>Install</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Download the files.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Copy <code class=\"language-text\">boxer.js</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">boxer.css</code>, and <code class=\"language-text\">close.png</code> into your project.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Include <code class=\"language-text\">boxer.js</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">boxer.css</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Wrap your target anchors in a container:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>boxer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>picture1.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>this is a picture<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>picture1_thumb.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>picture2.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>this is another picture<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>picture2_thumb.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Initialize it: <code class=\"language-text\">$(\".boxer\").boxer();</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Role</strong></p>\n<p>Sole author. I designed and built the plugin, its preview/overlay behavior, and the AJAX snippet support.</p>\n<p><strong>Links</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/chrisbautista/boxerjs\">Source on GitHub</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrisbautista.github.io/boxerjs/\">Live demo</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":1,"fields":{"slug":"/boxerjs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"BoxerJS","date":"March 02, 2015","isoDate":"2015-03-02","tags":["javascript","jquery","extension"],"featured_image":"/boxerjs_codespud.png","featured_image_attribution":null,"contentType":"works"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/boxerjs/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/construc-tables/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Go Nuts: ConstrucTables","contentType":"works","tags":["arduino","iot","rest-api"],"draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/morsecode-potato/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Morsecode-Potato","contentType":"works","tags":["reactjs","tailwind"],"draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1683739581","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}